The '''[[GCC Champions League]]''' ({{lang-ar|دوري أبطال الخليج للأندية}}), is an annually organized football league tournament for club of the [[Arabian Peninsula]].
The 2016 edition was set to be the 31st edition.<ref>https://instagram.com/p/3jd8Riog4P/</ref>
On August 6th 2015 it was announced that the competition would be postponed until February 2016 due to the suspension of [[Kuwait]] from [[FIFA]]. Later in January 2016 it was announced that the competition would not take place at all due to a lack of sponsorship. The next edition would therefore be held in 2017.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kooora.com/?n=459598&cz=8467&o=n8467|title=اللجنة التنظيمية تقرر تأجيل كأس الأندية الخليجية 31|language=Arabic|publisher=Kooora|date=12 January 2016|accessdate=23 January 2016}}</ref>
